      <title>苏纳克排除了 5 月 2 日英国大选的可能性，预示着今年晚些时候举行投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/sunak-rules-out-may-2-uk-election-signaling-vote-later-in-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相里希·苏纳克排除了 5 月 2 日举行英国大选的可能性，暗示将在今年晚些时候举行公众投票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/sunak-rules-out-may-2-uk-election-signaling-vote-later-in-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 18:47:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿巴斯任命巴勒斯坦投资基金负责人组建政府</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/abbas-names-palestine-investment-fund-chief-to-form-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴勒斯坦权力机构主席马哈茂德·阿巴斯任命巴勒斯坦投资基金主席组建新政府，该政府将在以色列与哈马斯战争结束后寻求重建加沙地带。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/abbas-names-palestine-investment-fund-chief-to-form-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 18:38:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国打击快时尚的法案扫清了第一道障碍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/french-bill-clamping-down-on-fast-fashion-clears-first-hurdle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国议会下院批准了政府支持的立法，旨在对快时尚施加惩罚和其他限制，因为它会对环境造成危害。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/french-bill-clamping-down-on-fast-fashion-clears-first-hurdle</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 18:28:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国在联合国推动全球人工智能监管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/us-pushes-for-global-ai-rules-at-un-as-regulations-lag-behind</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国在联合国提出了一项决议，提倡“安全、可靠和值得信赖”的人工智能系统，努力协调全球法规，旨在解决对该技术快速扩张的法律、国家安全和人权问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/us-pushes-for-global-ai-rules-at-un-as-regulations-lag-behind</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 18:01:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪的政党是现已被禁止的选举债券的最大受益者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/modi-s-party-biggest-beneficiary-of-now-banned-electoral-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据印度选举监管机构在全国大选前几周发布的数据，总理纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的印度人民党在过去五年中通过选举债券获得了近一半的政治捐款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/modi-s-party-biggest-beneficiary-of-now-banned-electoral-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 17:53:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉脱维亚总理称俄罗斯在乌克兰的胜利将影响美国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/russian-victory-in-ukraine-will-affect-us-latvian-premier-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拉脱维亚总理埃维卡·西利纳表示，如果俄罗斯不支持乌克兰，而俄罗斯在冲突中取得胜利，将会产生全球影响，包括美国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/russian-victory-in-ukraine-will-affect-us-latvian-premier-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 17:21:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴克莱银行表示，特朗普第二任期将引发美元上涨 3%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/second-term-trump-policies-spark-3-dollar-rally-barclays-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴克莱银行(Barclays Plc)外汇策略师表示，如果前总统唐纳德·特朗普(Donald Trump)在11月再次当选，基于他提出的增加关税、经济刺激和对北约承诺减弱的政策建议，美元将上涨3%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/second-term-trump-policies-spark-3-dollar-rally-barclays-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 17:06:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Milei 向阿根廷州长发送缩减改革法案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/milei-sends-scaled-back-reform-bill-to-argentina-s-governors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷总统哈维尔·米莱向该国州长分发了改革方案的新的精简版本，以期在重新提交国会之前赢得他们的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/milei-sends-scaled-back-reform-bill-to-argentina-s-governors</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 16:52:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于拜登反对协议，美国钢铁股连续第二天暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/biden-says-us-steel-should-remain-domestically-owned-operated</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国钢铁公司(United States Steel Corp.)连续第二天暴跌，此前美国总统乔·拜登表示，该公司应保留美国所有权，并反对日本新日铁公司(Nippon Steel Corp.)的收购，尽管这可能会触怒一个关键盟友。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/biden-says-us-steel-should-remain-domestically-owned-operated</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 11:10:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚因加沙抗议而被暂停组织起诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/columbia-sued-by-students-groups-suspended-over-gaza-war-protest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚大学因反对加沙战争的示威活动而被两个学生团体起诉，这两个团体去年被停课，这是该校因反犹太主义和巴勒斯坦权利等热门话题而面临的越来越多诉讼中的最新一起。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/columbia-sued-by-students-groups-suspended-over-gaza-war-protest</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 16:55:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
